T01D1119:67b-1: ni ru pa ma sta bam /
T01D1119:67b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1119:67b-5: gang zhig lta bas phongs pa yi //
T01D1119:67b-7: dngos po med pa'i don rig pas //
T01D1119:67b-8: dpe med khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T01D1119:67b-9: gang zhig khyod kyis cung zhig kyang //
T01D1119:67b-10: sangs rgyas spyan gyis ma gzigs pa //
T01D1119:67b-11: khyod kyis gzigs pa bla med de //
T01D1119:67b-12: de nyid don ni rig pa lags ;
T01D1119:67b-13: / don dam pa yi yod pa nyid //
T01D1119:67b-14: rtogs dang rtogs bya mi mnga' zhing //
T01D1119:67b-15: ae ma'o mchog tu rtogs dka' ba'i //
T01D1119:67b-16: chos nyid sangs rgyas rnams kyis rtogs //
T01D1119:67b-17: khyod kyis cung zhig ma bskyed cing //
T01D1119:67b-18: chos rnams bkag pa'ang ma lags la //
T01D1119:67b-19: mnyam pa nyid kyi lta ba yis //
T01D1119:67b-20: bla na med pa'i go 'phang brnyes //
T01D1119:67b-21: 'khor ba spangs par gyur pa yis //
T01D1119:67b-22: mya ngan 'das khyod mi bzhed kyi //
T01D1119:67b-23: 'khor ba ma dmigs pa nyid kyi //
T01D1119:67b-24: zhi de mgon po khyod kyis rtogs //
T01D1119:67b-25: khyod kyis kun nas nyon mongs dang //
T01D1119:67b-26: rnam byang ro gcig gyur rig pas //
T01D1119:67b-27: chos dbyings mngon par dbyer med pa //
T01D1119:67b-28: kun du rnam par dag par gyur //
T01D1119:67b-29: gtso bo khyod kyis 'ga' zhig tu //
T01D1119:67b-30: yi ge gcig kyang ma gsungs la //
T01D1119:67b-31: gdul bya'i 'gro ba ma lus pa //
T01D1119:67b-32: chos kyi char gyis tshim par mdzad //
T01D1119:67b-33: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i thugs mnga' khyod //
T01D1119:67b-34: phung po khams dang skye mched la //
T01D1119:68a-2: chos rnams kun la brten ma lags //
T01D1119:68a-3: mgon khyod sems can 'du shes kyis //
T01D1119:68a-4: 'jug pa kun du mi mnga' yang //
T01D1119:68a-5: sdug bsngal gyur pa'i sems can la //
T01D1119:68a-6: snying rje'i bdag nyid gyur pa'ang khyod //
T01D1119:68a-7: bde dang sdug bsngal de bzhin du //
T01D1119:68a-8: rtag mi rtag sogs la gtso khyod //
T01D1119:68a-9: de lta'i rnam rtog sna tshogs kyis //
T01D1119:68a-10: thugs ni chags par gyur ma lags //
T01D1119:68a-12: de bzhin khyod kyis gshegs pa'ang lags //
T01D1119:68a-13: 'ga' ru spungs pa ma mchis pa //
T01D1119:68a-14: de phyir don dam rig pa'ang lags //
T01D1119:68a-15: kun gyi rjes su zhugs gyur kyang //
T01D1119:68a-17: skye dang chos dang sku rnams kyang //
T01D1119:68a-18: thub chen khyod kyi bsam mi khyab //
T01D1119:68a-19: gcig dang gzhan pa rnams spangs pa //
T01D1119:68a-20: brag ca lta bu'i 'gro ba rnams //
T01D1119:68a-22: smad pa med pa khyod kyis rtogs //
T01D1119:68a-23: rtag dang chad pa dang bral zhing //
T01D1119:68a-24: mtshan nyid mtshon bya rnam spangs par //
T01D1119:68a-25: gtso bos rmi lam sgyu tshogs bzhin //
T01D1119:68a-26: 'khor ba nges par rtogs pa lags //
T01D1119:68a-27: bag chags gzhir gyur mthar thug pa'i //
T01D1119:68a-28: khyod kyis nyon mongs sdig pa spangs //
T01D1119:68a-29: nyon mongs nyid kyi rang bzhin yang //
T01D1119:68a-30: khyod kyis bdud rtsi nyid du bsgrubs //
T01D1119:68a-31: dpa' bo khyod kyis gzugs rnams kyis //
T01D1119:68a-32: mtshan ma med mthong gzugs med bzhin //
T01D1119:68a-33: mtshan gyis 'bar ba'i sku nyid kyang //
T01D1119:68a-34: gzugs su spyod yul nyid du mthong //
T01D1119:68a-35: gzugs su mthong bas mthong min yang //
T01D1119:68a-36: mthong ngo zhes ni rjod par byed //
T01D1119:68a-37: chos mthong bas ni shin tu mthong //
T01D1119:68a-38: chos nyid mthong ba ma yin no //
T01D1119:68a-39: khong stong khyod kyi sku la med //
T01D1119:68a-40: sha dang rus pa khrag med kyang //
T01D1119:68a-41: nam mkha'i dbang po'i gzhu bzhin du //
T01D1119:68a-42: khyod kyi sku ni ston par mdzad //
T01D1119:68a-43: sku la bsnyun med mi gtsang med //
T01D1119:68a-44: bkres dang skom pa 'byung med kyang //
T01D1119:68a-46: 'jig rten spyod pa'ang ston par mdzad //
T01D1119:68a-47: las kyi sgrib pa'i skyon rnams ni //
T01D1119:68a-48: sdig med khyod kyis kun spangs kyang //
T01D1119:68a-49: khyod kyis sems can rjes gzung phyir //
T01D1119:68a-50: las spangs par yang rab tu bstan //
T01D1119:68a-51: chos kyi dbyings la dbyer med phyir //
T01D1119:68b-0: gtso bo theg @68b dbyer ma mchis kyang //
T01D1119:68b-1: khyod kyi theg pa gsum bstan pa //
T01D1119:68b-2: sems can gzhug pa'i ched du lags //
T01D1119:68b-3: rtag cing brten la zhi ba yi //
T01D1119:68b-4: chos kyi rang bzhin khyod kyi sku //
T01D1119:68b-5: rgyal bas gdul bya 'gro ba'i phyir //
T01D1119:68b-6: khyod nyid mya ngan 'das par bstan //
T01D1119:68b-7: grangs med 'jig rten khams rnams su //
T01D1119:68b-8: 'das dang bltams dang mngon byang chub //
T01D1119:68b-9: 'khor ba'ang thar par mos rnams kyi //
T01D1119:68b-10: khyod la gus rnams kyis yang mthong //
T01D1119:68b-11: mgon po sems pa mi mnga' zhing //
T01D1119:68b-12: rnam rtog g-ye ba mi mnga' yang //
T01D1119:68b-13: khyod nyid dang gis 'jig rten la //
T01D1119:68b-15: de ltar bde gshegs yon tan tshad med bsam mi khyab //
T01D1119:68b-16: me tog gis brgyan pa las bsod nams gang thob par //
T01D1119:68b-17: gyur pa 'di ni sems can ma lus pa 'di
T01D1119:68b-18: dag / mchog tu rtogs dka' thub pa'i chos kyi
T01D1119:68b-19: snod gyur cig / dpe med par bstod pa slob
T01D1119:68b-20: dpon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so
T01D1119:68b-22: / // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po krishna pandi ta dang /
